---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <title>Manual Vivo™ — Grupo Caribe × Antemano</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="/logo-a.png" type="image/png" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Instrument+Serif:ital@0;1&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />

  <style>
    /* ── Reset & tokens ─────────────────────────────────────── */
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    :root {
      --c: #1A1A1A;
      --w: #FAFAFA;
      --ww: #FFFFFF;
      --g: #F3F3F3;
      --mid: #6B7280;
      --border: rgba(26,26,26,.10);
      --ease-out-expo: cubic-bezier(0.16,1,0.3,1);
      --ease-out-quart: cubic-bezier(0.25,1,0.5,1);
    }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%; }
    body {
      background: var(--ww);
      color: var(--c);
      font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
      -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
      text-rendering: optimizeLegibility;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }
    ::selection { background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; }
    :focus-visible { outline: 2px solid #1a1a1a; outline-offset: 3px; border-radius: 4px; }

    /* ── Typography helpers ──────────────────────────────────── */
    .si {
      font-family: 'Instrument Serif', Georgia, serif;
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 400;
      font-size: 1.06em;
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -.01em;
    }
    .eyebrow {
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.45);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .eyebrow-dark {
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--mid);
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }

    /* ── Container ───────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .container {
      max-width: 1100px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 0 1.5rem;
    }

    /* ── Sections ────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .s-dark  { background: var(--c);  color: #fff;      padding: 6rem 0; }
    .s-light { background: var(--w);  color: var(--c);  padding: 6rem 0; }
    .s-white { background: var(--ww); color: var(--c);  padding: 6rem 0; }
    .s-gray  { background: var(--g);  color: var(--c);  padding: 6rem 0; }

    /* ── Section headings ────────────────────────────────────── */
    .h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6.5vw, 5.5rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.0;
      letter-spacing: -.03em;
      max-width: 15ch;
    }
    .h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 4.5vw, 3.75rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -.025em;
      max-width: 20ch;
    }
    .h2-center { text-align: center; margin: 0 auto; }
    .section-sub {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: var(--mid);
      margin-top: .75rem;
      max-width: 44ch;
    }
    .section-sub-center { text-align: center; margin: .75rem auto 0; }

    /* ── Buttons ─────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .5rem;
      font-size: .95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: .85rem 1.75rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: transform .2s var(--ease-out-quart), box-shadow .2s var(--ease-out-quart), background .15s;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }
    .btn:hover  { transform: scale(1.025); }
    .btn:active { transform: scale(0.96); transition-duration: .08s; }

    .btn-light { background: #fff; color: var(--c); }
    .btn-light:hover { box-shadow: 0 12px 28px -8px rgba(0,0,0,.22); }

    .btn-dark { background: var(--c); color: #fff; }
    .btn-dark:hover { box-shadow: 0 12px 28px -8px rgba(0,0,0,.35); }

    .btn-outline-light {
      background: transparent;
      color: #fff;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.35);
    }
    .btn-outline-light:hover { border-color: #fff; background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); }

    /* ── Reveal animations ───────────────────────────────────── */
    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(24px);
      transition: opacity .7s var(--ease-out-expo), transform .7s var(--ease-out-expo);
    }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
    .reveal-d1 { transition-delay: .12s; }
    .reveal-d2 { transition-delay: .22s; }
    .reveal-d3 { transition-delay: .32s; }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    /* NAV                                                         */
    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    #pnav {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
      z-index: 100;
      padding: 1rem 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      transition: background .4s, backdrop-filter .4s, border-color .4s;
    }
    #pnav.scrolled {
      background: rgba(26,26,26,.82);
      backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);
    }
    .pnav-inner {
      max-width: 1100px;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 0 auto;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
    }
    .pnav-logo {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      letter-spacing: -.03em;
    }
    .pnav-label {
      font-size: .7rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.35);
    }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    /* S1: HERO                                                    */
    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    #hero {
      min-height: 100svh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      padding: 8rem 0 5rem;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    #hero::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%, rgba(255,255,255,.03) 0%, transparent 70%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .hero-tag {
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.35);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .75rem;
    }
    .hero-tag::before {
      content: '';
      display: block;
      width: 2rem;
      height: 1px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.25);
    }
    .hero-h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2.75rem, 7.5vw, 6.5rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: 1.0;
      letter-spacing: -.035em;
      color: #fff;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      max-width: 18ch;
    }
    .hero-sub {
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.8vw, 1.25rem);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
      max-width: 52ch;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .hero-teaser {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.45);
      max-width: 50ch;
      line-height: 1.65;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }
    .hero-scroll-hint {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 2rem;
      right: 2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .5rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.2);
      font-size: .7rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: .1em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }
    .hero-scroll-hint svg { animation: bounce 1.8s ease-in-out infinite; }
    @keyframes bounce {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(5px); }
    }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    /* S2: PROBLEM                                                 */
    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .prob-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
      .prob-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: start; }
    }
    .prob-body p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #4B5563;
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    }
    .prob-list {
      list-style: none;
      margin: 1rem 0 1.75rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: .9rem;
    }
    .prob-list li {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.6;
      padding-left: 1.5rem;
      position: relative;
    }
    .prob-list li::before {
      content: '—';
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      color: var(--c);
      font-weight: 700;
    }
    .prob-remate {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      color: var(--c);
      line-height: 1.65;
      border-left: 3px solid var(--c);
      padding-left: 1rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
    }
    .stat-chips {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .stat-chip {
      background: var(--c);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: .5rem;
    }
    .stat-chip-n {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -.04em;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .stat-chip-l {
      font-size: .8rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .stat-chip:nth-child(1) { grid-column: 1 / -1; background: var(--c); }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    /* S3: CALCULADORA                                             */
    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .calc-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      margin-top: 3.5rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 900px) {
      .calc-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; align-items: start; }
    }

    /* Inputs */
    .calc-inputs { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .input-group { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .5rem; }
    .input-label {
      font-size: .8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #374151;
      letter-spacing: .02em;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
    }
    .input-val {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: var(--c);
    }
    input[type="range"] {
      -webkit-appearance: none;
      appearance: none;
      width: 100%;
      height: 3px;
      background: #E5E7EB;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      cursor: pointer;
      outline: none;
    }
    input[type="range"]::-webkit-slider-thumb {
      -webkit-appearance: none;
      width: 18px; height: 18px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--c);
      border: 2px solid #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 1px 6px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform .15s;
    }
    input[type="range"]::-webkit-slider-thumb:hover { transform: scale(1.2); }
    input[type="range"]::-moz-range-thumb {
      width: 18px; height: 18px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--c);
      border: 2px solid #fff;
      cursor: pointer;
    }
    .input-hint {
      font-size: .72rem;
      color: #9CA3AF;
      font-style: italic;
    }

    /* Output */
    .calc-output {
      position: sticky;
      top: 6rem;
      background: var(--c);
      color: #fff;
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }
    .star-label-top {
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.4);
    }
    .star-number {
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 5rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -.04em;
      line-height: 1;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .star-sub {
      font-size: .85rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.45);
      margin-top: .25rem;
    }
    .breakdown { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
    .br-row { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .35rem; }
    .br-label-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: .78rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    .br-label-name { color: rgba(255,255,255,.65); }
    .br-label-val  { color: #fff; }
    .br-bar-bg {
      height: 4px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.12);
      border-radius: 9999px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .br-bar-fill {
      height: 100%;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.7);
      border-radius: 9999px;
      transition: width .6s var(--ease-out-expo);
      width: 0;
    }
    .calc-disclaimer {
      font-size: .72rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.3);
      line-height: 1.5;
      padding-top: 1rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
    }
    .calc-remate {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 52ch;
    }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    /* S4: WHY MANUALS FAIL                                        */
    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .fail-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 640px) { .fail-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
    @media (min-width: 900px) { .fail-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; } }
    .fail-card {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    .fail-card-n {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.15);
      letter-spacing: -.04em;
      margin-bottom: .75rem;
    }
    .fail-card-t {
      font-size: .95rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.7);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .fail-remate {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 52ch;
    }
    .fail-remate strong { color: #fff; }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    /* S5: SYSTEM / MODULAR EXPLORER                               */
    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .explorer-intro {
      margin-top: 3.5rem;
      display: grid;
      gap: 3rem;
    }
    .layers-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: .75rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 640px) { .layers-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
    .layer-card {
      border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
      transition: border-color .2s, background .2s;
    }
    .layer-card:hover { border-color: var(--c); background: rgba(26,26,26,.02); }
    .layer-n {
      font-size: 2rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: rgba(26,26,26,.12);
      letter-spacing: -.04em;
      line-height: 1;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .layer-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .3rem; }
    .layer-title { font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 800; color: var(--c); }
    .layer-desc  { font-size: .88rem; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.5; }

    /* Explorer */
    #explorer {
      margin-top: 4rem;
      background: var(--c);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .explorer-h {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.45);
      letter-spacing: .05em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: .75rem;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }
    .explorer-cols {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 700px) { .explorer-cols { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
    .explorer-col-title {
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.35);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    .sub-chips {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: .5rem;
    }
    .sub-chip {
      font-size: .8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: .45rem .9rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.55);
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: all .2s;
      user-select: none;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .4rem;
    }
    .sub-chip:hover { border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.4); color: rgba(255,255,255,.85); }
    .sub-chip.active {
      background: #fff;
      color: var(--c);
      border-color: #fff;
    }
    .sub-chip .chip-badge {
      font-size: .68rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.15);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
      padding: .1rem .4rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
    }
    .sub-chip.active .chip-badge {
      background: rgba(26,26,26,.1);
      color: var(--c);
    }
    .plat-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: .4rem;
    }
    .plat-item {
      font-size: .9rem;
      padding: .6rem .9rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.45);
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      transition: all .2s;
      cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none;
    }
    .plat-item:hover { color: rgba(255,255,255,.8); background: rgba(255,255,255,.05); }
    .plat-item.active {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.1);
      color: #fff;
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.15);
    }
    .plat-item.dimmed { opacity: .25; }
    .plat-item .plat-subs {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: .3rem;
      margin-top: .35rem;
    }
    .plat-sub-tag {
      font-size: .66rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      padding: .15rem .5rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.4);
      transition: all .2s;
    }
    .plat-sub-tag.highlight {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.2);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.85);
    }
    .explorer-punchline {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      font-size: .9rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.4);
      text-align: center;
    }
    .explorer-punchline strong {
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    .explorer-punchline.has-selection { color: rgba(255,255,255,.65); }
    .explorer-punchline.has-selection strong { font-size: 1.3rem; }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    /* S6: PRODUCCIÓN (star section)                               */
    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .prod-body {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.6);
      line-height: 1.7;
      max-width: 52ch;
      margin: 2rem 0;
    }
    .prod-body p + p { margin-top: 1rem; }
    .prod-features {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.07);
      border-radius: 20px;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 640px) { .prod-features { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
    @media (min-width: 900px) { .prod-features { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; } }
    .prod-feat {
      background: var(--c);
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: .75rem;
      transition: background .2s;
    }
    .prod-feat:hover { background: #252525; }
    .prod-feat-icon {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .prod-feat-title {
      font-size: .95rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.3;
    }
    .prod-feat-desc {
      font-size: .82rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.45);
      line-height: 1.55;
    }
    .prod-result {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 2rem;
      max-width: 56ch;
    }
    .prod-result p {
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.75);
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .prod-result strong { color: #fff; }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    /* S7: DEMO                                                    */
    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .demo-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
      margin-top: 3.5rem;
      align-items: center;
    }
    @media (min-width: 768px) { .demo-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
    .qr-mock {
      aspect-ratio: 1;
      max-width: 280px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      border: 2px dashed var(--border);
      border-radius: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 1rem;
      color: #9CA3AF;
      background: var(--g);
    }
    .qr-icon { font-size: 3rem; }
    .qr-label { font-size: .8rem; font-weight: 600; text-align: center; line-height: 1.5; }
    .demo-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.25rem; }
    .demo-step {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    .demo-step-n {
      width: 2rem;
      height: 2rem;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--c);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: .8rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .demo-step-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .25rem; padding-top: .25rem; }
    .demo-step-title { font-size: .95rem; font-weight: 700; color: var(--c); }
    .demo-step-desc  { font-size: .88rem; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.5; }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    /* S8: OFERTA                                                  */
    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    .offer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-top: 3.5rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 900px) { .offer-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; align-items: start; } }
    .offer-card {
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 2rem 1.75rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    .offer-card-1 {
      background: var(--w);
      border: 2px solid var(--c);
    }
    .offer-card-2 { background: var(--w); border: 1.5px solid var(--border); }
    .offer-card-3 { background: var(--c); color: #fff; }
    .offer-step {
      font-size: .72rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--mid);
    }
    .offer-card-3 .offer-step { color: rgba(255,255,255,.4); }
    .offer-h {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -.025em;
      line-height: 1.15;
    }
    .offer-card-3 .offer-h { color: #fff; }
    .offer-price {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -.03em;
      line-height: 1;
    }
    .offer-price-placeholder {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: .25rem .75rem;
      border: 1.5px dashed var(--border);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--mid);
    }
    .offer-card-3 .offer-price-placeholder {
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.2);
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
    }
    .offer-desc {
      font-size: .9rem;
      color: #4B5563;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .offer-card-3 .offer-desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,.6); }
    .offer-tag {
      font-size: .75rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      padding: .35rem .8rem;
      border-radius: 9999px;
      align-self: flex-start;
    }
    .offer-tag-risk {
      background: rgba(26,26,26,.08);
      color: var(--c);
    }
    .offer-anchor {
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      padding: 2rem;
      background: rgba(26,26,26,.04);
      border-radius: 16px;
      max-width: 56ch;
    }
    .offer-anchor p {
      font-size: 1rem;
      color: #374151;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .offer-anchor strong { color: var(--c); font-weight: 800; }
    #star-anchor {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--c);
      letter-spacing: -.03em;
    }
    .offer-property {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 16px;
      max-width: 56ch;
      font-size: .9rem;
      color: #4B5563;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .offer-property strong { color: var(--c); }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    /* S9: CTA FINAL                                               */
    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    #piloto {
      text-align: center;
    }
    .cta-big {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -.03em;
      color: #fff;
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      max-width: 20ch;
      margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
    }
    .cta-sub {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.5);
      max-width: 44ch;
      margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
      line-height: 1.65;
    }
    .cta-btns {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 1rem;
    }
    @media (min-width: 480px) { .cta-btns { flex-direction: row; justify-content: center; } }
    .cta-note {
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      font-size: .82rem;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.3);
      max-width: 44ch;
      margin: 1.5rem auto 0;
      line-height: 1.55;
    }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    /* S10: ABOUT FOOTER                                           */
    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    #about-footer {
      padding: 4rem 0;
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .about-inner {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 1rem;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }
    @media (min-width: 640px) {
      .about-inner {
        flex-direction: row;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }
    }
    .about-logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: var(--c); letter-spacing: -.04em; }
    .about-text { font-size: .85rem; color: #6B7280; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 52ch; }
    .about-link { color: var(--c); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none; }
    .about-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    /* PRINT LEAVE-BEHIND                                          */
    /* ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── */
    #print-page { display: none; }

    @media print {
      #pnav, #hero, #problema, #calculadora, #fallan, #sistema,
      #produccion, #demo, #oferta, #piloto, #about-footer {
        display: none !important;
      }
      #print-page {
        display: block !important;
        font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        padding: 2rem;
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .pr-logo { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -.04em; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
      .pr-date  { font-size: .75rem; color: #9CA3AF; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
      .pr-title { font-size: 2rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -.03em; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
      .pr-sub   { font-size: 1rem; color: #4B5563; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
      .pr-box {
        border: 2px solid #1a1a1a;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .pr-box-l { font-size: .72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: #9CA3AF; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
      .pr-star  { font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: -.04em; }
      .pr-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2.5rem; }
      .pr-step  { display: flex; gap: 1rem; align-items: flex-start; padding: 1.25rem; border: 1px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 12px; }
      .pr-step-n { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 900; color: #E5E7EB; flex-shrink: 0; }
      .pr-step-t { font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 700; }
      .pr-step-d { font-size: .82rem; color: #4B5563; line-height: 1.5; margin-top: .25rem; }
      .pr-cta    { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; text-align: center; padding: 1rem; background: #1a1a1a; color: #fff; border-radius: 10px; }
      .pr-foot   { margin-top: 2rem; font-size: .72rem; color: #9CA3AF; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #F3F3F3; padding-top: 1rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<!-- ─── NAVBAR ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<nav id="pnav">
  <div class="pnav-inner">
    <a href="/" class="pnav-logo">A.</a>
    <span class="pnav-label">Manual Vivo™ × Grupo Caribe</span>
    <a href="#piloto" class="btn btn-light" style="font-size:.8rem;padding:.6rem 1.25rem;">Quiero el Piloto</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ─── S1: HERO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="hero" class="s-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="hero-tag reveal">Grupo Caribe × Antemano</p>
    <h1 class="hero-h1 reveal reveal-d1">
      Cada vez que renuncia un cocinero, tu mejor receta se va <em class="si">con él.</em>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub reveal reveal-d2">
      Y no está anotada en ningún lado. Vive en su cabeza, en la de tu chef, en la de dos personas más. El día que faltan, el platillo sale distinto. O no sale.
    </p>
    <p class="hero-teaser reveal reveal-d2">
      Hay un costo en tu operación que no aparece en el P&L.<br>
      No lo ve tu contador. Nadie lo factura. Pero te cuesta más que cualquier proveedor.
    </p>
    <a href="#calculadora" class="btn btn-light reveal reveal-d3">
      Ver cuánto me está costando
      <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-scroll-hint" aria-hidden="true">
    <svg width="16" height="16" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
    <span>scroll</span>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── S2: PROBLEMA ─────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="problema" class="s-light">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow-dark reveal">Diagnóstico</p>
    <div class="prob-grid">
      <div>
        <h2 class="h2 reveal">
          No tienes un problema de capacitación.<br>
          Tienes un problema de <em class="si">memoria.</em>
        </h2>
        <div class="prob-body">
          <p>Tu conocimiento más valioso —cómo se hace cada platillo, exactamente igual, todos los días— vive en la memoria de poca gente. Y esa memoria renuncia, se enferma, se va a otro restaurante.</p>
          <p>Mientras tanto:</p>
          <ul class="prob-list">
            <li>El que entrena es tu persona más cara, fuera de la línea, repitiendo lo mismo con cada nuevo.</li>
            <li>El platillo sale distinto según quién esté en turno. El cliente lo nota.</li>
            <li>Cada cocinero porciona "al ojo". Ahí se va tu food cost, gramo por gramo, sin que lo veas.</li>
            <li>Y cuando cambias la carta, tardas semanas en que salga parejo en toda la cocina.</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="prob-remate">
            Lo normal es aceptar esto como "así es el negocio restaurantero".<br>
            No lo es. Es un costo que se puede medir. Y que se puede bajar.
          </p>
        </div>
        <a href="#calculadora" class="btn btn-dark" style="margin-top:2rem;">Medirlo con mis números →</a>
      </div>

      <div class="stat-chips reveal reveal-d2">
        <div class="stat-chip">
          <span class="stat-chip-n">75%</span>
          <span class="stat-chip-l">rotación anual promedio en la industria restaurantera mexicana</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-chip">
          <span class="stat-chip-n">3 sem</span>
          <span class="stat-chip-l">para que un cocinero nuevo opere al estándar del restaurante</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-chip">
          <span class="stat-chip-n">+3%</span>
          <span class="stat-chip-l">gap típico en food cost entre cocinas con y sin estándares documentados</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-chip">
          <span class="stat-chip-n">0</span>
          <span class="stat-chip-l">restaurantes que realmente usan sus manuales de capacitación</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── S3: CALCULADORA ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="calculadora" class="s-white">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow-dark reveal">Calculadora de impacto</p>
    <h2 class="h2 reveal reveal-d1">
      Mete tus números.<br>
      Mira lo que estás <em class="si">dejando en la mesa.</em>
    </h2>
    <p class="section-sub reveal reveal-d2">Sin trampa. Son tus cifras. Nosotros solo ponemos las fórmulas.</p>

    <div class="calc-layout">
      <!-- INPUTS -->
      <div class="calc-inputs">
        <div class="input-group reveal">
          <label class="input-label">
            Cocineros en cocina
            <span class="input-val" id="v-cocineros">8</span>
          </label>
          <input type="range" id="s-cocineros" min="2" max="40" value="8" step="1" />
          <span class="input-hint">¿Cuántas personas trabajan en tu cocina en total?</span>
        </div>

        <div class="input-group reveal reveal-d1">
          <label class="input-label">
            Contrataciones por año
            <span class="input-val" id="v-rotacion">6</span>
          </label>
          <input type="range" id="s-rotacion" min="1" max="30" value="6" step="1" />
          <span class="input-hint">¿Cuántos cocineros nuevos contratas en un año?</span>
        </div>

        <div class="input-group reveal reveal-d1">
          <label class="input-label">
            Días hasta que opera solo
            <span class="input-val" id="v-dias">21 días</span>
          </label>
          <input type="range" id="s-dias" min="7" max="60" value="21" step="1" />
          <span class="input-hint">¿Cuántos días tarda un nuevo en ser autónomo en su estación?</span>
        </div>

        <div class="input-group reveal reveal-d2">
          <label class="input-label">
            Costo-hora del entrenador
            <span class="input-val" id="v-hora">$120/hr</span>
          </label>
          <input type="range" id="s-hora" min="60" max="400" value="120" step="10" />
          <span class="input-hint">¿Cuánto te cuesta por hora la persona que entrena al nuevo?</span>
        </div>

        <div class="input-group reveal reveal-d2">
          <label class="input-label">
            Food cost actual vs. objetivo
            <span class="input-val" id="v-fc">35% vs 30%</span>
          </label>
          <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:.75rem;">
            <div>
              <input type="range" id="s-fc-actual" min="20" max="60" value="35" step="1" />
              <span class="input-hint">Actual</span>
            </div>
            <div>
              <input type="range" id="s-fc-obj" min="15" max="55" value="30" step="1" />
              <span class="input-hint">Objetivo</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="input-group reveal reveal-d2">
          <label class="input-label">
            Venta mensual de cocina
            <span class="input-val" id="v-venta">$300,000</span>
          </label>
          <input type="range" id="s-venta" min="50000" max="2000000" value="300000" step="10000" />
          <span class="input-hint">¿Cuánto vende tu cocina en un mes normal?</span>
        </div>

        <div class="input-group reveal reveal-d3">
          <label class="input-label">
            Platillos devueltos o rehechos / semana
            <span class="input-val" id="v-dev">5</span>
          </label>
          <input type="range" id="s-dev" min="0" max="30" value="5" step="1" />
          <span class="input-hint">Por inconsistencia, error de preparación o estándar diferente.</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- OUTPUT -->
      <div class="calc-output reveal reveal-d1">
        <div>
          <p class="star-label-top">Costo anual del sistema actual</p>
          <p class="star-number" id="star-num">$374,780</p>
          <p class="star-sub">por año — estimado con tus datos</p>
        </div>

        <div class="breakdown" id="breakdown">
          <div class="br-row">
            <div class="br-label-row">
              <span class="br-label-name">Capacitación</span>
              <span class="br-label-val" id="br-cap">$91,980</span>
            </div>
            <div class="br-bar-bg"><div class="br-bar-fill" id="bar-cap" style="width:0"></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="br-row">
            <div class="br-label-row">
              <span class="br-label-name">Rotación</span>
              <span class="br-label-val" id="br-rot">$30,000</span>
            </div>
            <div class="br-bar-bg"><div class="br-bar-fill" id="bar-rot" style="width:0"></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="br-row">
            <div class="br-label-row">
              <span class="br-label-name">Merma / food cost</span>
              <span class="br-label-val" id="br-mer">$180,000</span>
            </div>
            <div class="br-bar-bg"><div class="br-bar-fill" id="bar-mer" style="width:0"></div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="br-row">
            <div class="br-label-row">
              <span class="br-label-name">Devoluciones</span>
              <span class="br-label-val" id="br-dev">$72,800</span>
            </div>
            <div class="br-bar-bg"><div class="br-bar-fill" id="bar-dev" style="width:0"></div></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="calc-disclaimer">
          Estimado basado en benchmarks de la industria. Ajusta los sliders con tus cifras reales para mayor precisión.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="calc-remate reveal">
      Ese número de arriba es lo que cuesta el sistema actual. Cada año.<br>
      Hoy ya lo estás pagando — solo que no lo ves en ningún reporte.
    </p>
    <a href="#fallan" class="btn btn-dark reveal" style="margin-top:2rem;">Lo que sigue es cómo dejas de pagarlo →</a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ─── S4: POR QUÉ FALLAN LOS MANUALES ─────────────────────────────── -->
<section id="fallan" class="s-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow reveal">El problema con lo que existe</p>
    <h2 class="h2 reveal reveal-d1" style="color:#fff;">
      El 88 % de la gente que ve un manual de capacitación,<br><em class="si">lo odia.</em>
    </h2>
    <div class="fail-grid" style="margin-top:3rem;">
      {[
        { n: '01', t: 'Un PDF de 80 páginas que nadie abre. Si lo abren, no lo terminan. Si lo terminan, no lo aplican.' },
        { n: '02', t: 'Un video corporativo plano: cámara fija, cocinero hablando, 8 minutos, cero edición. Nadie lo ve completo.' },
        { n: '03', t: 'Una carpeta en Drive con archivos sin orden. Nadie sabe qué buscar ni dónde. El que sabe, ya renunció.' },
        { n: '04', t: 'Tu personal ya consume short-form vertical todo el día. Darles capacitación de 2009 es garantizar que no la usen.' },
        { n: '05', t: 'El entrenamiento verbal no escala. Cada quien lo aprende diferente. El estándar muere con quien lo enseñó.' },
        { n: '06', t: 'Un sistema que nadie usa no es un sistema. Es un cementerio de buenas intenciones.' },
      ].map(c => (
        <div class="fail-card reveal">
          <div class="fail-card-n">{c.n}</div>
          <p class="fail-card-t">{c.t}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
    <p class="fail-remate reveal">
      <strong>Una carpeta de videos en Drive no es un sistema.</strong><br>
      Es un cementerio de buenas intenciones.<br>
      Nosotros no hacemos eso.
